originalText.text: Do not rent a car from here. Hours are unreliable and numbers to call are always busy. We rented a zipcar from here and checked the hours well before. We showed up to get our zipcar and waited over an hour to retrieve our vehicle. Another guys was also there to return a zipcar and said he had been waiting already for 45m before me showed up. Bad service.

originalText.text: I would have given them 0 stars if I could. The female parking attendant was incredibly rude and raising her voice when I was disputing a ridiculous up charge. She then proceeded to speak to the other attendants about me in Spanish (not knowing I am fluent) and even when the one attendant tried to just charge me the fair price, she insisted I pay an additional $20. She is a terrible person and an awful representative for this parking garage. I would NEVER go back there again.

originalText.text: Easy to see right off of 55th street servicing Midtown and the adjoining areas of Manhattan.   Moderately clean facilities.   New York City prices so bring your credit cards.   Staff is ok.   Popular during night times and the weekends.   Give it a try and you decide.

originalText.text: I had a reservation with ParkWhiz but when I arrived the attendant said the garage was full and he cancelled. Thankfully ParkWhiz refunded. There were several people standing there waiting for their cars and it looked like they were going nowhere fast. Won’t reserve there again.
